{"tid":2196810,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"劉鳴煒相信海洋公園不可能在一年內轉虧為盈","createTime":"2020-09-10T07:15:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-10T15:53:48.000Z","uid":184679,"like":9,"dislike":156,"uniUserReply":116,"replies":[{"pid":"22cd6e066bb2554465631d4dfc6db07883f0b276","tid":2196810,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T07:15:08.000Z","msg":"海洋公園行政總裁陳善瑜表示，公園的經營環境持續嚴峻，由年初疫情以來，公園只營業了52天，令財政壓力百上加斤。她說未來會投放更多資源在本地市場，提升本地客的比例，這有利公園長期持續發展。<br />\n<br />\n海洋公園主席劉鳴煒說，他和陳善瑜的任期只有一年，相信公園不可能在一年內轉虧為盈，但希望在任期內為公園尋找出路。他形容疫情期間公園的人流和收入跌幅達9成，雖然公園已經「慳得就慳」，但仍然有人工、保育動物、維修機動遊戲和機器的開支。<br />\n<br />\n另外，劉鳴煒透露，水上樂園會在今年年底完工，但無論如何不會於今年內開始運作，至於何時起可運作，有待重新審視。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1548861-20200910.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1548861-20200910.htm&d=8aZ3B%2FsgtJclBbEiVdGGE7PGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=0724d909\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1548861-20200910.htm&h=f8fa2172\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1548861-20200910.htm</a>"},{"pid":"5b8f22842798a7d6ceeb0f257d2669fce24003c6","tid":2196810,"uid":95577,"like":229,"dislike":1,"score":228,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T07:17:06.000Z","msg":"含撚啦你<br />\n問政府攞左幾十億仲講咁多廢話<br />\n無能力就唔好做<br />\n私人公司一早炒左"},{"pid":"29ff8724c7b885225050958fcc4ded23bd75d7e4","tid":2196810,"uid":522,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T07:17:43.000Z","msg":"又可以繼續出糧 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfb58fb347aa2651a5d54286d3fe88d13e97c6fe","tid":2196810,"uid":58209,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T07:18:45.000Z","msg":"執柒左佢啦"},{"pid":"f4db030703d5f842ad1bffcb4ae30c4d1754ad4a","tid":2196810,"uid":89608,"like":54,"dislike":0,"score":54,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T07:18:56.000Z","msg":"佢唔覺得醜嗰度好野"},{"pid":"35