s/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dfa823629c488263667326f1a52b2be71c24a5d","tid":2196810,"uid":232167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"22cd6e066bb2554465631d4dfc6db07883f0b276","tid":2196810,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T07:15:08.000Z","msg":"海洋公園行政總裁陳善瑜表示，公園的經營環境持續嚴峻，由年初疫情以來，公園只營業了52天，令財政壓力百上加斤。她說未來會投放更多資源在本地市場，提升本地客的比例，這有利公園長期持續發展。<br />\n<br />\n海洋公園主席劉鳴煒說，他和陳善瑜的任期只有一年，相信公園不可能在一年內轉虧為盈，但希望在任期內為公園尋找出路。他形容疫情期間公園的人流和收入跌幅達9成，雖然公園已經「慳得就慳」，但仍然有人工、保育動物、維修機動遊戲和機器的開支。<br />\n<br />\n另外，劉鳴煒透露，水上樂園會在今年年底完工，但無論如何不會於今年內開始運作，至於何時起可運作，有待重新審視。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1548861-20200910.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1548861-20200910.htm&d=8aZ3B%2FsgtJclBbEiVdGGE7PGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=0724d909\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1548861-20200910.htm&h=f8fa2172\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1548861-20200910.htm</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T09:07:33.000Z","msg":"//水上樂園會在今年年底完工//<br />\n冬天先起完，搵鬼玩咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲話重新審視，水費都虧死你，係開就等4月la"},{"pid":"45fe91e845b3652d39e9e5ed3c1048a9e1768bfe","tid":2196810,"uid":121076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f4db030703d5f842ad1bffcb4ae30c4d1754ad4a","tid":2196810,"uid":89608,"like":54,"dislike":0,"score":54,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T07:18:56.000Z","msg":"佢唔覺得醜嗰度好野"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T09:08:45.000Z","msg":"佢如果係叻仔，以大劉為人華置至少留個cfo比佢啦，點會放佢出黎?"}]}